<div class="toplang">
<p><span>Available Languages: </span><a href="./en/dns-caveats.html" title="English">&nbsp;en&nbsp;</a> |
<a href="./ja/dns-caveats.html" hreflang="ja" rel="alternate" title="Japanese">&nbsp;ja&nbsp;</a> |
